ABOUT
=====

Rubyk is a Rubic cube simulator written in Ruby with SDL and OpenGL.

KEYBOARD CONTROL
================

 * Arrow Keys: Rotate the cube
 * Escape: Exit program
 * CTRL+S: Scamble cube
 * W: Rotate white face clockwise
 * w: Rotate white face counter-clockwise
 * G: Rotate green face clockwise
 * g: Rotate green face counter-clockwise
 * R: Rotate red face clockwise
 * r: Rotate red face counter-clockwise
 * B: Rotate blue face clockwise
 * b: Rotate blue face counter-clockwise
 * O: Rotate orange face clockwise
 * o: Rotate orange face counter-clockwise
 * Y: Rotate yellow face clockwise
 * y: Rotate yellow face counter-clockwise
